#31601
Edris lamplighter man~
Edris the Lamplighter~
A thin man with dressed in a warm, fur-lined jacket stands here gazing through the trees.
~
Edris is a thin, hardened man with laugh lines that indicate he once lived a
happy life.  He lives a life of solitude now, with his loyal dog for
companionship.  He is dressed in warm clothing to battle the sharp winds the
whistle through the treetops.  He is the Lamplighter that attends the beacon's
light and ensures it stays lit for travelers to gauge.  He welcomes visitors
as it breaks the monotony of his life.  
~
