#31602
sleeping hound asha~
Asha the hound~
A small hound lays curled up by the stove half-awake.
~
   She is an older dog, likely a hound mutt.  She dozes lightly in front of
the burning stove.  Her fur is medium length and the dark brown is beginning
to gray around her snout.  Even though she appears to be sleeping, you can
tell she is aware of her owner, Edris at all times.  
~
