#31603
dosfigured man Wren~
Wren the hermit~
A man with a horribly disfigured face stares at you while warming his hands on the stove.
~
   The pain this man must have endured as the trauma that caused the massive
scarring on his face is unimaginable.  The scarring itself leaves only minor
spots of untouched skin.  The long-healed, if you could call it healed, scars
run down into the collar of the shapeless shirt that he wears.  The man is
very thin and looks at you with bright, green eyes that sparkle with
intelligence.  He spends his days in solace, writing into large leather bound
journals.  
~
