#31649
short faced bear~
the Gigantic Short-Faced Bear~
An enormous bear whose fur is matted in blood stands on its hind legs furiously.
~
   This horrible creature is not like any bear you've ever encountered.  Its
limbs are significantly longer than a typical grizzly bear or brown bear.  
Weighing in around the same at almost one ton, it is a bit more slender and
gracile.  The Short-faced bear is built for speed and the destruction of life.
~
